statements.sql: select `photos`.`filename`, `photos`.`name`, `photos`.`description`, `photo_albums`.`folder_id` from `photos` inner join `photo_albums` on `photo_albums`.`id` = `photos`.`photo_album_id` where `photos`.`slider` = '1' order by `photos`.`position` desc, `photos`.`created_at` desc

select `photo_albums`.`id`, `photo_albums`.`name`, `photo_albums`.`description`, `photo_albums`.`folder_id`, (select filename from photos WHERE album_cover=TRUE and photos.photo_album_id=photo_albums.id LIMIT 1) AS album_image, (select filename from photos WHERE photos.photo_album_id=photo_albums.id ORDER BY position ASC, id ASC LIMIT 1) AS album_image_first from `photo_albums` limit 8

select `video_albums`.`id`, `video_albums`.`name`, `video_albums`.`description`, `video_albums`.`folder_id`, (select youtube from videos WHERE album_cover=TRUE and videos.video_album_id=video_albums.id LIMIT 1) AS album_image, (select youtube from videos WHERE videos.video_album_id=video_albums.id ORDER BY position ASC, id ASC LIMIT 1) AS album_image_first from `video_albums` limit 8
